Lineage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

scalacv began in 2015 as `mcallisto/scalacv` by Mario Càllisto
(https://github.com/mcallisto), a Scala 2.11 wrapper over the OpenCV 3.0 Java
API. That repository carried no license file, and neither did this fork before
2026 — so the original work remained all rights reserved.

The present library is therefore a clean-room rewrite. It shares no code with
the 2015 sources: the effect model, the module layout and the underlying Java
API all changed, and every call site was rewritten. The lineage is recorded here
because it is a fact about where the project came from, and because the original
author's work is why it exists at all — not because any code survives.

Two of the 2015 example programs descended in turn from:

  * rladstaetter/isight-java  — https://github.com/rladstaetter/isight-java
  * chimpler/blog-scala-javacv — https://github.com/chimpler/blog-scala-javacv

Both are likewise unlicensed. No code from either is present here.

